8_5	0.0	Dr. Timothy McAlindon, a Boston University rheumatologist and lead author of the analysis, said his conclusions are ''a little more positive'' than the ''profound skepticism which has existed''.
8_6	0.0	''I'm not actively recommending'' chondroitin and glucosamine, ''but I certainly don't discourage people from trying them provided they're cognizant of the available data,'' McAlindon said.
