14_0	0.0	This isn't the way medical science is supposed to work.
14_1	0.0	A remedy used to treat creaky bones in horses and dogs works so well that humans start taking it.
14_2	0.0	It gets hyped in a best-selling book on arthritis and the number of users skyrockets.
