14_6	0.0	The early results of research, including one study just published and another due out soon, suggest the treatment actually does ease joint pain and may even forestall further cartilage damage.
14_7	0.0	The promising research is bound to make the hard-to-pronounce potions, which are available over the counter, even more wildly popular.
